<h4 id="betting">Betting</h4>
<p>Betting is allowed up to 10 seconds prior to the race start. Betting options for future races of the current race days remain open.</p>
<p>The following race betting options are available:</p>
<ol>
<li><p><strong>Win</strong> – bet on the selected bikes to win the race. (e.g., Bike No.1 finishes 1st).</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Place</strong> (1-2) – bet on the selected bike to finish 1st or 2nd position in a race. (e.g., Selection 1: Bike No.1 finishes 1st or 2nd).</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Show</strong> (1-3) – bet on the selected bike to finish 1st, 2nd or 3rd position in the race. (e.g., Selection 1: Bike No.1 finishes 1st, 2nd or 3rd).</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Even/Odd</strong> – bet on No. Even (2/4) or No.Odd (1/3) to finish 1st position in a race.</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Over/Under</strong> – bet on the winner is over or under No.3.5 (Selection Over: Bike No.3, No.4 or No.5 finishes 1st; Selection Under: Bike No.1, No.2 or No.3 finishes 1st).</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Exacta</strong> – bet on the 2 bikes finishing in 1st and 2nd positions, in the order predicted. Both predictions must be correct for the bet to win. (e.g., Selection 1, 2: Bike No.1 finishes 1st, Bike No.2 finishes 2nd).</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Quinella</strong> – bet on the 2 bikes you expect to finish 1st and 2nd in any order. Both predictions must be correct for the best to win. (e.g., Selection1&amp;2: Bike No.1 and No.2 finish 1st and 2nd in any order).</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Trifecta</strong> – bet on the 3 bikes you expect to finish 1st, 2nd and 3rd in the correct order. All three predictions must be correct for the bet to win. (e.g., Selection 1, 2, 3: Bike No.1 finishes 1st, Bike No.2 finishes 2nd, Bike No.3 finishes 3rd).</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="your-bets">Your bets</h4>
<p>As you make your bet selections by clicking on the odds relating to the bet you wish to place, the betslip will open. Once you have made all your selections, enter your stake in the betslip Stake field and click on Bet. Your bet will be placed.</p>
<p>Virtual Bike Racing bets cannot be combined in the same betslip with bets placed on real sport events.</p>
<p>If your bet is successful, your winnings will automatically be credited to your account.</p>
<p>To see the list of your Virtual Bike bets, please go to Virtuals page and click on &quot;MY BETS&quot; next to &quot;BETSLIP&quot;. You will find a list of all bets you have placed. Also you can find details in the &quot;Bets History&quot; in the bottom of &quot;MY BETS&quot;.</p>
